---
title: Dukkah Crusted Cod with Spiced Veggies and Roasted Garlic Mayo
description: Dukkah is a mix of nuts, seeds and spices, and its flavour works perfectly as a crust for delicate, mild-tasting fish like cod as well as giving it a satisfyingly crispy top! Serve with tender roasted veggies drizzled in garlic mayo. Simply delicious!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/dukkah-crusted-cod-cf7d9648-011a28e3.jpg
